<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>堆排 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E5%A0%86%E6%8E%92/</link><description>堆排 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E5%A0%86%E6%8E%92/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>排序算法</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E4%B8%8E%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95/%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E4%B8%8E%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95/%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="排序算法">排序算法</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：排序算法的选择取决于数据规模、内存限制和稳定性需求，快速排序是通用场景首选，归并排序适合链表和外部排序，堆排序适合内存受限且需持续获取TopK的场景。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="常用排序算法在时间复杂度空间复杂度和稳定性三个维度各有侧重没有绝对最优">常用排序算法在时间复杂度、空间复杂度和稳定性三个维度各有侧重，没有绝对最优</h2>
<h3 id="算法对比总览">算法对比总览</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>算法</th>
          <th>平均时间</th>
          <th>最坏时间</th>
          <th>空间</th>
          <th>稳定性</th>
          <th>适用场景</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>快速排序</td>
          <td>O(n log n)</td>
          <td>O(n²)</td>
          <td>O(log n)栈</td>
          <td>不稳定</td>
          <td>通用数组排序</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>归并排序</td>
          <td>O(n log n)</td>
          <td>O(n log n)</td>
          <td>O(n)</td>
          <td>稳定</td>
          <td>链表排序、外部排序</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>堆排序</td>
          <td>O(n log n)</td>
          <td>O(n log n)</td>
          <td>O(1)</td>
          <td>不稳定</td>
          <td>TopK、内存受限</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>插入排序</td>
          <td>O(n²)</td>
          <td>O(n²)</td>
          <td>O(1)</td>
          <td>稳定</td>
          <td>小规模、近乎有序</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>希尔排序</td>
          <td>O(n^1.3)</td>
          <td>O(n²)</td>
          <td>O(1)</td>
          <td>不稳定</td>
          <td>中等规模</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>选择排序</td>
          <td>O(n²)</td>
          <td>O(n²)</td>
          <td>O(1)</td>
          <td>不稳定</td>
          <td>理论意义</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>冒泡排序</td>
          <td>O(n²)</td>
          <td>O(n²)</td>
          <td>O(1)</td>
          <td>稳定</td>
          <td>教学演示</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>计数排序</td>
          <td>O(n+k)</td>
          <td>O(n+k)</td>
          <td>O(k)</td>
          <td>稳定</td>
          <td>数据范围小</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>桶排序</td>
          <td>O(n)</td>
          <td>O(n²)</td>
          <td>O(n+k)</td>
          <td>稳定</td>
          <td>数据均匀分布</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>基数排序</td>
          <td>O(d(n+k))</td>
          <td>O(d(n+k))</td>
          <td>O(n+k)</td>
          <td>稳定</td>
          <td>固定位数整数</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
